title: 1987 - Guns N' Roses - Appetite For Destruction [German GED 2414
description: This isn't just another Appetite For Destruction upload, it was mastered in 1990 by Barry Diament.  His mastering for cd was only used on this German edition.  A blu-ray audio is coming out of this album and I guarantee this smokes it.  When you compare it to other versions you'll hear better instrument separation and an overall smoothness that's better sounding than the other versions
